	<component id="ID_Body_txt01">
		<text><![CDATA[<textformat blockindent='-14' ><li>HSRP defines a group of routers - one active and one standby.</li><li>Virtual IP and MAC are shared between the two routers.</li><li>To verify HSRP state, use the <font face="_typewriter"><b>show standby</b></font> command.</li><li>HSRP is Cisco proprietary.</li><li>VRRP is a standard protocol.</li></textformat>]]></text>
